.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH cdf-run 1  "cdf-run "
.SH NAME
cdf\-run \- Execute a governed resource run
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcdf run\fR [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-resource\fR] [\fB\-\-pipeline\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-to\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-target\fR] [\fB\-\-package\-id\fR] [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-checkpoint\-id\fR] [\fB\-\-unicode\fR] [\fB\-\-jobs\fR] [\fB\-\-loop\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIRESOURCE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Execute a governed resource run
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress progress and non\-primary success narration
.TP
\fB\-\-resource\fR \fI<RESOURCE>\fR
Resource identifier (compatibility form)
.TP
\fB\-\-pipeline\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Pipeline identifier compatibility option
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Show evidence detail; repeat for diagnostics
.TP
\fB\-\-color\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Color policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-to\fR \fI<DEST>\fR
Destination URI or cursor upper bound, as shown in usage
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-color\fR
Compatibility alias for \-\-color never
.TP
\fB\-\-target\fR \fI<TARGET>\fR
Destination target/table compatibility option
.TP
\fB\-\-package\-id\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Explicit package identifier for script compatibility
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Progress policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-checkpoint\-id\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Explicit checkpoint identifier for script compatibility
.TP
\fB\-\-unicode\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Unicode policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-jobs\fR \fI<N>\fR
Maximum concurrent jobs
.TP
\fB\-\-loop\fR
Continue polling for work
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIRESOURCE\fR]
Resource identifier
